# features/
#
# Feature-scoped modules. Each subdirectory corresponds to a distinct
# application domain and contains its own components, hooks, and types.
#
# Structure (to be populated during page migration):
#   features/
#   ├── dashboard/     ← Dashboard components, hooks, and types
#   ├── onboarding/    ← Onboarding flow components
#   ├── pricing/       ← Pricing page components and pricing logic
#   ├── checkout/      ← Checkout and Stripe Elements components
#   ├── admin/         ← Admin panel components
#   ├── brand/         ← Brand Center components
#   └── work/          ← Portfolio / case study components
#
# This co-location pattern keeps feature-specific code self-contained
# and simplifies future refactoring.
